{"title":"关于小河","authors":["苏金伞"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏金伞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河发源于我的梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河发源于我的梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流经我的血管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注入黎明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此小河是隐秘的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏在夜的衣袂下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用手指捺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会感到它的跳动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水是浅浅的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掩不住星星；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷穗会沉在里面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星和谷粒难以分清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注入黎明后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就消失了自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片澄澈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像刚睁开的大眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河发源于母亲的童年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另一条小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发源于母亲的童年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲未嫁时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成天在河里洗衣裳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棒槌砸着砧石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很远就能听见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到我童年时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河就成了我的同伴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走亲戚时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在河边踏着青草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚱蜢从脚前飞起又落下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但不敢踢石子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踢破了鞋尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会受到母亲的埋怨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而河心里的水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淌过圆圆的石子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溅出的水花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像蚱蜢的翅膀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跳到河水里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石子就搔我的脚心；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要不溅湿裤腿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲就不会责备。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去了童年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲也死了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河也因之消失。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以后见了大河见了大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再也找不到小河处所。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另一条小河不知发源哪里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另一条小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不知发源在哪里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在深山里行走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下总脱不开小河的缠绕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时正走着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河忽然在面前闪现，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一把剑斜刺里插来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无法防备也无法躲闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时不知不觉地踩在脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像踩上一条小蛇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随即蜿蜒着爬走了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时横在前面的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是深深的潭湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好从旁边绕过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕到有桥的地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者绕到半山间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时却是在石子下潜流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过去也不湿鞋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出清脆的响声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像小妹妹在洗盘盏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过很多回还往复，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不知到底走了多远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最后终于走出了山腹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小河不知什么时候不见了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1988年8月20日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}